577
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:13,440
[Duke's Mansion]

578
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:14,140
Father.

579
00:29:14,630 --> 00:29:15,550
It's so late.

580
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:17,640
Why did you call me back in such a hurry?

581
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,440
Lu Rongchang has been arrested.

582
00:29:19,790 --> 00:29:21,070
So what?

583
00:29:21,430 --> 00:29:22,070
Father.

584
00:29:22,090 --> 00:29:23,420
Your disciples are all over the world.

585
00:29:23,420 --> 00:29:25,150
Why are you worried because of him? He's just the director

586
00:29:25,150 --> 00:29:28,410
of the Market Affairs Department, a low-ranked official.

587
00:29:30,940 --> 00:29:32,480
It's all because of you.

588
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,120
I...

589
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:37,130
Why are you blaming me?

590
00:29:37,190 --> 00:29:38,550
If you hadn't been soft-hearted

591
00:29:38,550 --> 00:29:39,670
and let Xu Muchen go,

592
00:29:39,670 --> 00:29:41,670
His Majesty wouldn't have decided to investigate the case of the map thoroughly

593
00:29:41,670 --> 00:29:44,200
and Lu Rongchang wouldn't have got arrested.

594
00:29:45,950 --> 00:29:46,810
Sorry I made the mistake.

595
00:29:46,810 --> 00:29:47,570
Sorry?

596
00:29:49,070 --> 00:29:52,200
The problem won't be solved just because you said sorry.

597
00:29:52,670 --> 00:29:53,670
What should we do?

598
00:29:53,990 --> 00:29:54,710
Are you going to send me to jail

599
00:29:54,710 --> 00:29:56,770
so Lu Rongchang won't be imprisoned?

600
00:29:56,830 --> 00:29:59,090
I wish you could go to jail instead of him.

601
00:30:02,990 --> 00:30:04,590
Lu Rongchang has been arrested.

602
00:30:04,590 --> 00:30:06,990
The maps were all confiscated by Xu Muchen.

603
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:11,780
Only you

604
00:30:11,800 --> 00:30:13,930
can get the maps out of the capital now.

605
00:30:14,910 --> 00:30:15,870
Me?

606
00:30:15,870 --> 00:30:17,590
Yes, you'll do it.

607
00:30:19,670 --> 00:30:20,550
But, Father.

608
00:30:21,190 --> 00:30:23,200
Gongyang Maocai has got

609
00:30:23,230 --> 00:30:25,560
all the passes and piers heavily guarded.

610
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:26,990
All the officials will be searched.

611
00:30:26,990 --> 00:30:29,390
His men even forced officials to take off their underpants.

612
00:30:29,390 --> 00:30:31,430
How can I take the maps out of the capital under these circumstances?

613
00:30:31,430 --> 00:30:32,710
Transporting the maps without permission

614
00:30:32,710 --> 00:30:34,970
is a treasonable act and a capital crime.

615
00:30:47,630 --> 00:30:48,710
Su Jinning.

616
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:52,300
If the maps can't be transported to them,

617
00:30:53,040 --> 00:30:56,000
your sister will die.

618
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,030
Jinzhen.

619
00:31:00,430 --> 00:31:02,070
Do you think your sister ran away

620
00:31:02,070 --> 00:31:03,310
to avoid the marriage?

621
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,990
She was detained as a hostage.

622
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:07,510
If we don't transport the maps out of the capital,

623
00:31:07,510 --> 00:31:09,510
they will kill Jinzhen.

624
00:31:13,550 --> 00:31:14,990
You really want to see your sister

625
00:31:14,990 --> 00:31:17,630
lose her life

626
00:31:18,790 --> 00:31:21,750
because of your hesitation?

627
00:31:37,780 --> 00:31:38,710
Are you blind?

628
00:31:38,710 --> 00:31:39,770
You bumped into me.

629
00:31:40,580 --> 00:31:41,660
Shut up!

630
00:31:41,680 --> 00:31:43,330
Do you know who my young master is?

631
00:31:43,330 --> 00:31:44,530
I don't care who he is.

632
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:45,550
He bumped into me.

633
00:31:47,310 --> 00:31:48,310
Darn it.

634
00:31:49,650 --> 00:31:50,450
Young Master.

635
00:31:51,100 --> 00:31:51,900
Young Master.

636
00:31:52,610 --> 00:31:53,340
Are you okay?

637
00:31:54,790 --> 00:31:55,540
I'm fine.

638
00:31:55,960 --> 00:31:57,850
You go back first. I'll take a walk alone.

639
00:31:57,850 --> 00:31:58,650
Young Master.

640
00:32:01,550 --> 00:32:04,180
[Elegant Residence in Spring Sunshine]

641
00:32:09,630 --> 00:32:11,210
My husband has left to deal a case again?

642
00:32:11,210 --> 00:32:11,890
Yes.

643
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,200
Let me tell you.

644
00:32:13,230 --> 00:32:15,790
Yesterday, Young Master led the officers of Zichen Department

645
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,250
and scored a huge success.

646
00:32:17,390 --> 00:32:19,950
They caught Lu Rongchang,

647
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:21,800
the traitor who colluded with our enemies.

648
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:23,270
Lu Rongchang wanted to resist.

649
00:32:23,270 --> 00:32:24,870
He brought over hundred men and fought back.

650
00:32:24,870 --> 00:32:27,000
But in the end, Young Master and his men

651
00:32:27,120 --> 00:32:29,390
defeated them easily.

652
00:32:29,820 --> 00:32:30,970
He hasn't fully recovered yet.

653
00:32:30,970 --> 00:32:33,170
He shouldn't have done that last night.

654
00:32:34,310 --> 00:32:36,360
Is Young Master one of the real men

655
00:32:36,640 --> 00:32:38,430
in the storybooks?

656
00:32:41,510 --> 00:32:42,510
I also heard that

657
00:32:42,750 --> 00:32:44,270
they not only found the mastermind

658
00:32:44,270 --> 00:32:45,430
of the case of the map

659
00:32:45,630 --> 00:32:48,390
but also found out how Moon Star Herbs were smuggled.

660
00:32:48,390 --> 00:32:49,070
Really?

661
00:32:49,430 --> 00:32:50,560
What happened next?

662
00:32:51,280 --> 00:32:53,880
Then Young Master Gongyang stole the thunder.

663
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:56,030
He's so bad.

664
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:14,910
Master.

665
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:26,350
Xu Muchen wanted to investigate Lu Rongchang.

666
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:28,950
Why didn't you tell me about it earlier?

667
00:33:29,050 --> 00:33:31,320
I never asked about his work.

668
00:33:31,400 --> 00:33:33,000
What about the jade pendant?

669
00:33:35,190 --> 00:33:37,510
I'm sorry I haven't found it yet.

670
00:33:41,960 --> 00:33:42,510
Fine.

671
00:33:43,660 --> 00:33:45,190
I'll give you another task.

672
00:33:46,350 --> 00:33:47,710
Zichen Department has got the evidence

673
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:49,170
of Lu Rongchang's crimes.

674
00:33:50,380 --> 00:33:52,040
Go and steal the evidence now.

675
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:53,820
Master.

676
00:33:54,160 --> 00:33:55,280
I don’t understand.

677
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:56,510
You must know the harms of the Moon Star Herb

678
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:58,080
better than me.

679
00:33:58,100 --> 00:34:00,560
You said it could help the people of Taizhou.

680
00:34:00,890 --> 00:34:02,720
But it cannot solve the problem completely and will only make things worse.

681
00:34:02,720 --> 00:34:04,260
It may even do serious harm to the society.

682
00:34:04,260 --> 00:34:05,500
I have my reasons.

683
00:34:05,970 --> 00:34:07,830
You'll understand in the future.

684
00:34:13,510 --> 00:34:14,190
Rong.

685
00:34:15,210 --> 00:34:17,409
You're my best disciple.

686
00:34:18,350 --> 00:34:20,230
Although we are master and disciple,

687
00:34:20,230 --> 00:34:22,270
I see you as my own daughter.

688
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:26,600
Don't let me down.

689
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:30,350
I understand.

690
00:34:41,380 --> 00:34:43,400
This is a thing given to you by your father before he died.

691
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:44,570
To you,

692
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:47,120
this is more important than your life, right?

693
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:50,550
This jade pendant is indeed more important to me than is my life.

694
00:34:50,550 --> 00:34:52,360
But only when you keep it

695
00:34:53,560 --> 00:34:54,820
can I not feel worried.

696
00:35:02,510 --> 00:35:03,580
Do you think

697
00:35:03,620 --> 00:35:05,560
Watermill is a bad organization?

698
00:35:06,270 --> 00:35:07,280
I'm not sure.

699
00:35:08,100 --> 00:35:08,830
Why not?

700
00:35:09,260 --> 00:35:11,520
If those from Watermill were bad people,

701
00:35:12,210 --> 00:35:13,350
Willow Leaf Thief Liu

702
00:35:13,350 --> 00:35:16,360
wouldn't have used darts to save me on the execution ground.

703
00:35:16,360 --> 00:35:17,840
If my guess is right,

704
00:35:18,530 --> 00:35:20,550
those from Watermill and Moyan

705
00:35:21,010 --> 00:35:22,940
were fooled and used by bad people.

706
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,720
Although we are master and disciple,

707
00:35:27,720 --> 00:35:29,720
I see you as my own daughter.

708
00:35:31,600 --> 00:35:33,040
Don't let me down.

709
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:39,960
You're back.

710
00:36:02,270 --> 00:36:03,180
What's wrong?

711
00:36:03,830 --> 00:36:05,430
Is something bothering you?

712
00:36:06,490 --> 00:36:07,290
Nothing.

713
00:36:12,130 --> 00:36:13,320
I'm your husband.

714
00:36:13,700 --> 00:36:14,710
I know you well.

715
00:36:18,590 --> 00:36:21,720
You're injured but you're still working to solve cases.

716
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:23,590
I feel unhappy about it.

717
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:28,410
It's okay.

718
00:36:28,730 --> 00:36:29,400
I'm fine.

719
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:33,330
Xiao Qiu told me

720
00:36:33,790 --> 00:36:36,430
the mastermind of the case of the map has been found.

721
00:36:36,430 --> 00:36:40,090
But Young Master Gongyang took the credit and stole your thunder.

722
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:44,330
Don't worry, Madam.

723
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:46,130
He won't be able to steal my thunder.

724
00:36:46,130 --> 00:36:47,460
I have the key evidence.

725
00:36:49,770 --> 00:36:50,610
That's good.

726
00:37:07,630 --> 00:37:10,150
[Zichen Department]

727
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:23,130
[Uphold justice without compromise]

728
00:37:50,230 --> 00:37:52,830
The Moon Star Herbs were smuggled in large quantities.

729
00:37:52,830 --> 00:37:56,430
A great many people must have died because of the Moon Star Herbs.

730
00:37:58,780 --> 00:37:59,340
No.

731
00:37:59,680 --> 00:38:01,680
How can I help them do the evil deeds?

732
00:38:07,620 --> 00:38:09,620
The Ministry of Justice told me that

733
00:38:09,790 --> 00:38:11,790
Lu Rongchang only admitted that he had committed tax evasion

734
00:38:11,790 --> 00:38:14,320
and said he knew nothing about anything else.

735
00:38:14,490 --> 00:38:15,320
Muchen.

736
00:38:15,430 --> 00:38:16,750
We don't have the solid evidence

737
00:38:16,750 --> 00:38:18,990
to prove that Lu Rongchang is the culprit of the case of smuggling the maps.

738
00:38:18,990 --> 00:38:20,430
He would say his subordinates

739
00:38:20,430 --> 00:38:23,230
smuggled prohibited goods to make illegal money.

740
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:24,450
Don't worry.

741
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:27,410
We have the maps they were trying to smuggle.

742
00:38:27,410 --> 00:38:28,590
The evidence is solid.

743
00:38:28,590 --> 00:38:30,170
Though he kept denying the accusations, it would be useless.

744
00:38:30,170 --> 00:38:30,730
Yes.

