00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,000
Young Master.

773
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,240
Why are you back?

774
00:41:34,270 --> 00:41:36,530
Shouldn't you be on night shift tonight?

775
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:52,430
I missed you.

